" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/central-university-of-technology-cut-online-application\/#Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_CUT_admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CUT admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CUT admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80723462\">About the Central University of Technology (CUT) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80723463\"><strong>How to Apply for CUT Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80723464\">Documents Required for CUT Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80723465\">CUT Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80723466\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80723467\">Applying for Financial Assistance in CUT<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80723468\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CUT admission 2024?<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-central-university-of-technology-cut-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_Central_University_of_Technology_CUT_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80723462\"><\/a>About the Central University of Technology (CUT) Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the Central University of Technology(CUT) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80723463\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for CUT Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cut.ac.za\/application-process\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/li>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-cut-admission-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_CUT_Admission_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80723464\"><\/a>Documents Required for CUT Admission Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"cut-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CUT_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80723465\"><\/a>CUT Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee of R100 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R300<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80723466\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>31 October 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-cut\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_CUT\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80723467\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in CUT<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nsfas.org.za\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">portal<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-cut-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_CUT_admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80723468\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CUT admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cut.ac.za\/application-process\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"CUT Online Application 2024 for Admission into Central University of Technology, CUT Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1147,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1146"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1146"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1146\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1146"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1146"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1146"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}